   <head>A FLOWER, Painted by SIMON VARELST.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="sestet">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">fam'd  this little Wonder drew;</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">vouchsaf'd the growing Work to view:</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Finding the Painter's Science at a Stand,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">The Goddess snatch'd the Pencil from his Hand;</l>
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">And finishing the Piece, She smiling said;</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Behold One Work of Mine, that ne'er shall fade.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
